#   vendor/agy (~164 MB binary), vendor/frida-gum (devkit), vendor/uapi (Linux UAPI
#   headers), vendor/antigravity.so (compiled LD_PRELOAD shim).
antigravity/vendor/
# generated from symbols.json at build time:
antigravity/src/symbols_gen.h
antigravity/symbols/goresym.json
